================================================================================
LICENSING OVERVIEW
================================================================================

Agus Maps Flutter is released under the Apache License 2.0. This plugin
incorporates code and dependencies from various open-source projects, each
with their own licensing terms.

IMPORTANT: The information in this file is provided for informational purposes
only and does not constitute legal advice. We strongly recommend consulting
with a qualified legal professional to understand how these licenses apply to
your specific use case, especially for commercial applications.

Below you will find:
- Core project licenses (CoMaps, Organic Maps, MAPS.ME)
- OpenStreetMap data licensing (ODbL)
- Third-party library licenses
- Sample attribution text (for reference only)

Please perform your own due diligence to ensure compliance with all applicable
licenses for your intended use.

================================================================================
CoMaps (https://comaps.app/)
================================================================================
Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0
Copyright (c) CoMaps Contributors

CoMaps is a fork of Organic Maps, which is itself a fork of MAPS.ME.
CoMaps is actively developed with a focus on community-driven improvements.

Repository: https://codeberg.org/comaps/comaps

================================================================================
Organic Maps (https://organicmaps.app/)
================================================================================
Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0
Copyright (c) Organic Maps OÜ

Organic Maps is a privacy-focused, offline maps application.

ATTRIBUTION REQUEST (Courtesy, not legally required):
Please include a visible, human-readable mention of the "Organic Maps Project"
and a clickable link to https://organicmaps.app in any derived works.

================================================================================
MAPS.ME
================================================================================
Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0
Copyright (c) 2020 My.com B.V. (Mail.Ru Group)
Copyright (c) MapsWithMe GmbH

The original MAPS.ME project from which Organic Maps and CoMaps descend.

================================================================================
OpenStreetMap Data
================================================================================
Map data © OpenStreetMap contributors
Licensed under the Open Database License (ODbL)
https://www.openstreetmap.org/copyright

The map data used in MWM files is derived from OpenStreetMap and is available
under the Open Database License. For more information, see:
https://opendatacommons.org/licenses/odbl/

REQUIRED ATTRIBUTION:
You must display "© OpenStreetMap contributors" wherever map data is shown.
This is typically done as an overlay on the map or in your app's credits.

ODbL allows commercial use but requires:
- Attribution (as above)
- Share-Alike for the DATABASE only (not your app code)
- Keep the data open if you redistribute modified map data

Note: Using MWM files in your app does NOT require you to open-source your app.
The Share-Alike only applies if you modify and redistribute the map data itself.

