FONTS (bundled with CoMaps data)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Most fonts use the SIL Open Font License (OFL), which is permissive and allows
commercial use with attribution.

Khmer OS Font
  License: LGPL 2.1
  Copyright: 2005 Danh Hong, Open Forum of Cambodia
  
  Notes: LGPL for fonts is generally safe because font embedding is considered
  "mere aggregation" rather than creating a derivative work. Your app code
  remains unaffected.

Various other fonts: SIL Open Font License (OFL)
  - Permissive, allows commercial use
  - Requires attribution if redistributing the font files themselves

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
