================================================================================
LICENSE COMPATIBILITY SUMMARY
================================================================================

License Type          | Commercial Use | Attribution Required | Copyleft
----------------------|----------------|---------------------|----------
Apache 2.0            | ✓ Yes          | ✓ Yes (NOTICE file) | No
MIT                   | ✓ Yes          | ✓ Yes (copyright)   | No
BSD-3-Clause          | ✓ Yes          | ✓ Yes (copyright)   | No
Boost Software 1.0    | ✓ Yes          | No (in binaries)    | No
FreeType License      | ✓ Yes          | ✓ Yes (docs)        | No
zlib License          | ✓ Yes          | No                  | No
ICU License           | ✓ Yes          | ✓ Yes (copyright)   | No
SIL OFL (fonts)       | ✓ Yes          | ✓ Yes (if bundling) | No
ODbL (map data)       | ✓ Yes          | ✓ Yes (required)    | Data only*

* ODbL Share-Alike applies to the database/data only, not your application code

