ATTRIBUTION CONSIDERATIONS
================================================================================

The following are common attribution requirements found in the licenses used
by this project and its dependencies. This list is provided for informational
purposes only—please review each license directly and consult with a legal
professional to determine your specific obligations.

COMMON REQUIREMENTS (verify with original licenses):
1. Apache 2.0 typically requires inclusion of LICENSE and NOTICE files
2. OpenStreetMap data (ODbL) typically requires visible attribution
3. FreeType License (FTL) includes an attribution clause
4. Various MIT/BSD licenses typically require copyright preservation

ORGANIC MAPS REQUEST (Courtesy):
The Organic Maps project requests (but does not legally require) a visible
mention of "Organic Maps Project" with link to https://organicmaps.app

Please refer to the individual license texts for authoritative requirements.

